section.section:
Notice provided under this subsection shall state:
The date, time, place, and nature of the hearing;
The legal authority and jurisdiction of the Administration to hear the matter;
The nature of the proposed action that the Administration is to consider;
That a copy of the hearing procedures is available on request and the cost to obtain a copy;
The right of the victim's representative to be present at the hearing;
The right of the victim's representative to submit a written statement for consideration by the Administration at the hearing; and
The right of the victim's representative to make an oral statement for consideration by the Administration at the hearing.
